pe="person" ref="#pmb10863">Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></rs> u. die <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13923 #pmb2668 #pmb2534" subtype="implied">Kinder</rs>.<lb/>Ihre<signed>Olga.</signed></closer><p><date>23. 1. 10.</date></p></div></body><back><listPerson><tei:person xml:id="pmb2173">
